    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "这道题的精髓在于<strong>逆向思考</strong>：既然碎片是由不断切割得到的，那么拼回原矩形就是合并的逆过程。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "每次切割要么水平（保持宽度不变，分割高度），要么垂直（保持高度不变，分割宽度），因此合并时只能将<strong>具有相同高度</strong>或<strong>相同宽度</strong>的两个矩形拼在一起，且它们的另一边之和等于新矩形的对应边长。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "直接模拟这个过程即可。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tll h, w, n; cin >> h >> w >> n;\n\tvar p = vector<pll>(n + 1);\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cin >> p[i].px >> p[i].py;\n\n\tvar mph = HashMap<ll, set<int>>();\n\tvar mpw = HashMap<ll, set<int>>();\n\tvar se = set<int>();\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tconst var& [x, y] = p[i];\n\t\tmph[x].insert(i), mpw[y].insert(i);\n\t\tse.insert(i);\n\t}\n\n\tvar ans = vector<pll>(n + 1);\n\tll nowh = h, noww = w;\n\tll nowx = 1, nowy = 1;\n\twhile (se.size()) {\n\t\tint id = -1;\n\t\tbool h = 0;\n\t\tif (mph.count(nowh)) {\n\t\t\twhile (mph[nowh].size()) {\n\t\t\t\tvar now = mph[nowh].begin();\n\t\t\t\tif (se.count(*now)) {\n\t\t\t\t\tid = *now;\n\t\t\t\t\th = 1;\n\t\t\t\t\tbreak;\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\telse mph[nowh].erase(now);\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\tif (mph[nowh].empty())mph.erase(nowh);\n\t\t}\n\t\tif (id == -1 and mpw.count(noww)) {\n\t\t\twhile (mpw[noww].size()) {\n\t\t\t\tvar now = mpw[noww].begin();\n\t\t\t\tif (se.count(*now)) {\n\t\t\t\t\tid = *now;\n\t\t\t\t\tbreak;\n\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\telse mpw[noww].erase(now);\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\tif (mpw[noww].empty())mpw.erase(noww);\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tans[id] = { nowx, nowy };\n\t\tse.erase(id);\n\t\tif (h) {\n\t\t\tmph[nowh].erase(id);\n\t\t\tnowy += p[id].py;\n\t\t\tnoww -= p[id].py;\n\t\t}\n\t\telse {\n\t\t\tmpw[noww].erase(id);\n\t\t\tnowx += p[id].px;\n\t\t\tnowh -= p[id].px;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cout << ans[i].px << ' ' << ans[i].py << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
